text: Cincinnata konduensis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Breuning in 1935. It is known from the Democratic Republic of the Congo.BioLib.cz - Cincinnata konduensis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1935
